\end{aligned}
\]

---

### 2. Apply the relation  

\[
\begin{aligned}
P_2 &= 24\ \text{lb·in}^{-2}\times\frac{308.15\ \text{K}}{268.15\ \text{K}}\\[2mm]
    &= 24\ \text{lb·in}^{-2}\times 1.1492\\[2mm]
    &\approx 27.6\ \text{lb·in}^{-2}
\end{aligned}
\]

